    • Uses of BaseClientBuilder in com.azure.storage.blob

      Subclasses of BaseClientBuilder in com.azure.storage.blob 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  BaseBlobClientBuilder<T extends BaseClientBuilder<T>>
      RESERVED FOR INTERNAL USE ONLY Base builder for Azure Storage Blobs.
      class  BlobClientBuilder
      This class provides a fluent builder API to help aid the configuration and instantiation of BlobClients and BlobAsyncClients when buildClient and buildAsyncClient as called respectively.
      class  BlobContainerClientBuilder
      Fluent ContainerClientBuilder for instantiating a BlobContainerClient or BlobContainerAsyncClient using BlobContainerClientBuilder.buildClient() or BlobContainerClientBuilder.buildAsyncClient() respectively.
      class  BlobServiceClientBuilder
      Fluent BlobServiceClientBuilder for instantiating a BlobServiceClient or BlobServiceAsyncClient using BlobServiceClientBuilder.buildClient() or BlobServiceClientBuilder.buildAsyncClient() respectively.

    • Uses of BaseClientBuilder in com.azure.storage.blob.specialized

      This class provides a fluent builder API to help aid the configuration and instantiation of specialized Storage Blob clients, AppendBlobClient, AppendBlobAsyncClient, BlockBlobClient, BlockBlobAsyncClient, PageBlobClient, and PageBlobAsyncClient.
